com.attivio.sdk.geo

Class Point

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.attivio.sdk.geo.Point
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<Point>

    public class Point
extends Object
implements Cloneable, Comparable<Point>, Serializable
    Represents an x,y pair of doubles. This x,y pair can be used to represent coordinates for geo-based or other calculations.
